{
  "texts": [
    "They obtained the data from Cohen et al. [14] and the Kaggle repository.",
    "There were three classes in the dataset: COVID-19, Pneumonia, and Normal.",
    "The dataset is divided into three groups: training, validation, and testing, with respective ratios: 70%, 10%, and 20%.",
    "The average scores for recall, precision, and f1-score are 0.96, 0.96, and 0.95, respectively.Amir et al.",
    "designed a model named FCOD (Fast COvid Detector) [20]."
  ]
}